[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0260","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0260.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0117","title":"IBM AIX passwd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 passwd 命令存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于 passwd 程序在处理用户密码更改操作时未充分检查权限，本地普通用户可通过执行特制的 passwd 命令利用该漏洞获取 root 权限。攻击者需要拥有本地系统访问权限，无需身份认证即可提权至 root，从而完全控制系统。该漏洞影响早期版本的 AIX 操作系统，CVSS v2 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0117"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1992-03-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.490","remediation":"立即安装 IBM AIX 对应版本的 APAR 安全补丁（如 APAR IX47474 或更新版本），或升级至 AIX 4.1 及以上已修复版本。临时缓解措施可移除 passwd 命令的 SUID 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/passwd），但可能导致普通用户无法自行修改密码，需通过 root 管理员代为操作。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0117"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0260.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1341","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1341.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1121","title":"IBM AIX UUCP 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"UUCP（Unix-to-Unix Copy Protocol）在 AIX 3.2 之前版本的默认配置存在权限控制缺陷，本地攻击者可利用该配置漏洞直接获取 root 用户权限。该漏洞源于 UUCP 服务的文件权限和默认设置不当，攻击者仅需拥有系统本地访问权限即可实施提权攻击，无需其他认证条件。影响范围包括 AIX 3.2 之前版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1121"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1992-03-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:45.900","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 3.2 及以上版本，或修改 UUCP 配置文件（/etc/uucp/*）权限，限制非授权用户对 UUCP 程序的访问，移除 uucp 用户组中不必要的本地用户，并确保 uucp 相关 SUID 程序仅对 root 可执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1992-06.html","http://www.osvdb.org/891","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/38","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/554","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1121.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1121","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1121.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1121.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hpvq-q2w4-5255/GHSA-hpvq-q2w4-5255.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1121.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--82250b08-0a3b-45ce-88b9-a5c4e2c6cf17.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/network-security/index.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1341.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0927","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0927.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0627","title":"AIX rexd 服务认证弱漏洞","description":"AIX 系统上的 rexd（远程执行守护进程）服务默认启用，该服务使用基于主机名/IP 地址的弱认证机制，未对用户身份进行加密验证。远程攻击者可通过伪造源地址或利用信任关系绕过认证，直接向目标系统发送执行命令请求，导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响多个 AIX 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害严重。建议禁用 rexd 服务或配置严格访问控制列表。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0627"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1992-03-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:45.213","remediation":"关闭并禁用 AIX 系统的 rexd 服务（执行 `stopsrc -s rexd` 并将 `/etc/inetd.conf` 中 rexd 行注释掉后重启 inetd），或在防火墙/TCP Wrapper 的 `/etc/hosts.allow`、`/etc/hosts.deny` 中限制仅可信主机可访问 512 端口，禁止将 rexd 暴露于不可信网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0627","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4d7236390d3d65194e590e3c8620543620af3984/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0627.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0627","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0627.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6d3a932c05085f06507d23e5a0893fa8fe64ce42/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0627.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3jw7-6432-3rpc/GHSA-3jw7-6432-3rpc.json","https://github.com/NetBSD/pkgsrc-wip/blob/c422e48dc56726d2d6118a1549ab8a7864e96b47/sara/PLIST","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_rexd.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/berez23/canvas/blob/cb306a9d8b1d8a743049a29164e6d324f8dabbfa/exploits/remote/unix/rexd/rexd.py","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c23ad3c1-73a9-4c28-89b9-830a2ebc7be7.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0927.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1312","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1312.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1059","title":"AT&T TCP/IP 4.0 (SVR4) rexecd 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"AT&T TCP/IP 4.0 远程执行守护进程（rexecd）在多种 SVR4 系统上存在命令注入漏洞。该守护进程在处理远程执行请求时，未对传入的命令参数进行充分校验与过滤，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者可构造恶意请求，使 rexecd 以目标服务权限执行任意系统命令。影响范围涵盖运行 AT&T TCP/IP 4.0 的各 SVR4 类操作系统。攻击者只需能够与目标主机的 rexec 服务（TCP 512 端口）建立网络连接，并发送特制的执行请求即可完成利用，无需本地账户，CVSS 评分高达 10.0，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1059"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1992-02-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.173","remediation":"升级到 AT&T TCP/IP 4.0 的官方修复补丁版本，或停用 rexecd 服务（执行 `chkconfig rexec off` 并 kill 进程）。在防火墙/边界路由器上阻断 TCP 512 端口的入站连接，禁止来自不可信网络的 rexec 访问，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1992-04.html","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/3159.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/36","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1059.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1059","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1059.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3d905f6009ce1a0cb55b6b90198454d955586615/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1059.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4wjm-7g55-8frc/GHSA-4wjm-7g55-8frc.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1059.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/network-security/index.md","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/alegalanr/CyberMind/blob/c76c4e9bd6dd54b56cfe16f2210c2aa8c44c215c/code/database/dump.sql"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1312.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1292","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1292.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1032","title":"Digital Equipment Corporation Ultrix LAT/Telnet 网关(lattelnet) 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Ultrix 4.1 和 4.2 系统中的 LAT/Telnet 网关程序 lattelnet 存在特权提升漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的网络请求或命令，利用该网关在处理 LAT 与 Telnet 协议转换过程中的安全缺陷，在受影响的 Ultrix 系统上获取 root 权限，进而完全控制服务器。该漏洞影响所有运行 Ultrix 4.1 和 4.2 版本的平台，攻击无需任何凭据且利用条件简单，CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级为严重。CERT/CC 已发布安全公告 CA-1991-11 对此漏洞进行预警并披露修复方案。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1032"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1991-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.827","remediation":"升级 Digital Ultrix 至 4.3 或后续已修复版本（官方已移除 lattelnet 缺陷代码）；如暂无法升级，应立即在 inetd.conf 中禁用 lattelnet 服务并重启 inetd，同时用防火墙限制仅可信内网主机访问 23 端口作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/b-36.shtml","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1991-11.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/26","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/584","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/457d74301bd08d78bede177295a6ca646467d2a7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1032.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1032","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1032.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1032.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mjqg-8q9p-p7qh/GHSA-mjqg-8q9p-p7qh.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1032.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6a49b822-cf69-4257-98d3-80f16473afdb.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1292.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0338","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0338.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0167","title":"Sun SunOS NFS 文件句柄可猜测漏洞","description":"SunOS 系统中 NFS（网络文件系统）的文件句柄生成算法存在可预测性缺陷，远程攻击者可通过猜测或暴力枚举有效文件句柄的方式，绕过访问控制直接读取或修改 NFS 导出的文件系统中的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露和未授权访问。该漏洞影响 SunOS 多个版本，利用难度较低，无需身份认证即可实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0167"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1991-12-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:44.670","remediation":"升级 SunOS 到已修复该问题的推荐补丁（如 SunOS 4.1.x 对应补丁 ID 100482-xx 及以上版本）；配置 NFS 导出时启用 `root_squash`、`nosuid` 选项，对所有导出文件系统禁用 `insecure` 标志；在路由/防火墙上限制 2049 (NFS)、111 (portmapper) 端口的访问来源，仅允许可信客户端 IP；对于可挂载的导出目录，设置为只读（ro）以降低未授权写风险。如果迁移到 Solaris，建议升级至 Solaris 7 及以上版本并安装相应内核补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0167"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0338.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0749","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0749.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0498","title":"TFTP 路径限制绕过信息泄露漏洞","description":"TFTP（Trivial File Transfer Protocol）服务未配置为在受限目录中运行，导致远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过TFTP协议读取目标系统中任意可访问文件，包括密码文件、配置文件等敏感信息。该漏洞广泛影响早期Unix/Linux系统及嵌入式设备中默认配置的TFTP服务，攻击者只需知道目标IP地址并发送TFTP读取请求即可实施信息窃取，利用难度极低。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0498"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1991-09-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.613","remediation":"将 TFTP 服务配置为在 chroot 隔离目录中运行（如 /tftpboot），限制文件访问范围；在防火墙上禁止 TFTP 端口（UDP 69）对外开放，仅允许受信 IP 访问；如非必要，建议停用 TFTP 改用 SFTP/SCP 等加密文件传输协议。确保 TFTP 进程以低权限用户（如 nobody）运行，避免以 root 权限执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0498"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0749.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1328","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1328.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1090","title":"NCSA Telnet 默认配置远程文件读取与修改漏洞","description":"NCSA Telnet 软件包（Macintosh 和 PC 版本）存在默认配置不当的安全漏洞。其配置文件即使在未设置 'ftp=yes' 参数的情况下仍会错误地启用 FTP 服务，导致未经身份认证的远程攻击者能够直接通过该 FTP 服务读取和修改目标系统上的任意文件，严重危害系统数据的机密性和完整性。该漏洞影响 NCSA Telnet for Macintosh 和 PC 版本，无需任何认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1090"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1991-09-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.053","remediation":"在 NCSA Telnet 配置文件中显式添加 \"ftp=no\" 行以禁用默认启用的 FTP 服务，或升级到已修复此问题的最新版本；如无法升级，在防火墙层面阻止外部对 21/TCP 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施，并考虑迁移到 SSH 等加密远程访问方案以彻底规避风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1991-15.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1844"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1328.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1293","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1293.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1034","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1728,\"inputTokens\":9040,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10788}}","description":"AT&T System V Release 4（SVR4）操作系统的 login 程序存在权限提升漏洞，其实现在处理用户身份认证与登录会话初始化时存在缺陷，本地已登录的普通用户可利用该缺陷绕过正常的权限检查，将自身权限提升至 root 或等效特权。该漏洞仅影响运行 AT&T SVR4 及其衍生系统的本地环境，攻击者需先获得目标主机的本地访问权限（如一个低权限 shell 账号）方可利用。由于漏洞位于本地登录组件，攻击无需网络参与，但要求攻击者能够在目标系统上执行本地命令，属于典型的本地权限提升（LPE）类漏洞，可被用于完全控制系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1034"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1991-05-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:34.080","remediation":"升级到已修复该 login 漏洞的 AT&T System V Release 4 最新维护补丁或迁移至受支持的 Unix 系统；临时缓解措施为限制普通用户本地登录权限、将 /bin/login 文件权限设为 0755 且属主为 root、并通过审计日志监控异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1991-08.html","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/b-28.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/23","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/583","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f56f639de76f94fc0aef783754a3de16fea7357b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1034.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1034","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1034.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/be19cdaa6196942fd4096a42a1eaf047a8584298/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1034.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wqcg-hqq4-gw67/GHSA-wqcg-hqq4-gw67.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154600_154700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1034.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0e5f4f26-3faf-401c-ad46-0d388ce4dee9.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/NVDFeatureAnalysis/blob/493a57a415cc110f9945148abd717eeb92f6ca7e/originalDataset/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1293.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1243","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1243.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1123","title":"Sun SunOS 4.1.1 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.1 系统中在安装 Sun Source (sunsrc) 磁带时，会将 /usr/release/bin/makeinstall 和 winstall 程序设置为 setuid root 权限。本地普通用户可利用这些 setuid 程序以 root 身份执行任意操作，从而获取系统最高权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.1.1 版本，攻击者需要本地访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1123"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1991-05-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.150","remediation":"立即移除 /usr/release/bin/makeinstall 和 /usr/release/bin/winstall 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /usr/release/bin/makeinstall /usr/release/bin/winstall。如非必要，直接卸载 Sun Source (sunsrc) 软件包。建议升级至 Solaris 2.6 及以上版本，该版本已移除存在风险的 setuid 安装工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/107&type=0&nav=sec.sba","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1991-07.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/21","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/22","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/582","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19042","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1123.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1123.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1123","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1123.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1123.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4538-g7mm-6mqj/GHSA-4538-g7mm-6mqj.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/21/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1123.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000015.txt","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/network-security/index.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1243.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1386","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1386.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1193","title":"NeXT NeXTstep 权限提升漏洞","description":"NeXT NeXTstep 2.1 及更早版本中存在权限配置不当漏洞。系统默认创建的 \"me\" 用户被赋予了 wheel 组成员权限，该组成员可直接使用 su 命令切换为 root 超级用户。攻击者只需获取 \"me\" 用户的登录凭据（如通过弱口令猜测或社会工程学手段），即可利用该配置缺陷提升至 root 权限，完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 NeXT NeXTstep 2.1 及之前所有版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1193"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1991-05-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:54.997","remediation":"建议立即迁移至现代操作系统（如 macOS/Linux），NeXT NeXTstep 已停止维护无补丁。若必须继续使用，请编辑 /etc/group 将 me 用户从 wheel 组移除，并执行 `passwd -l me` 锁定该账户，同时限制 su 命令仅允许管理员组使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1991-06.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/20","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/581","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e8d44fc9434dcaf08511a3267e0bf049a6756de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1193.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1193","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1193.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1193.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h2w4-25qf-688g/GHSA-h2w4-25qf-688g.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_500_600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1193.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-266.txt","https://github.com/aciborowska/jingo/blob/c1a21f041501d5e6653f2e09046a5524af7274ea/datasets/corley/zookeeper/queries/long/2952.txt","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000014.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1386.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1255","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1255.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1194","title":"Digital Ultrix /usr/bin/chroot 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Digital Ultrix 4.0 和 4.1 系统中 /usr/bin/chroot 命令因安装权限配置不当，导致本地普通用户可利用该程序获取 root 权限。chroot 机制本用于限制进程的文件系统访问范围，但由于其可执行文件权限设置过于宽松，攻击者在获得低权限本地访问后，可通过 chroot 命令绕过隔离机制并提升至 root 权限，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞无需远程网络访问，仅需本地账户即可完成利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1194"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1991-05-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"修复 /usr/bin/chroot 权限配置：执行 chmod u-s /usr/bin/chroot 移除 setuid 权限位，并设置权限为 chmod 750 /usr/bin/chroot 以限制仅 root 组可执行。Digital 已发布 Ultrix 4.2 及以上版本修复该问题，建议升级至最新补丁集。在无法升级的旧系统上应严格控制本地用户访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1991-05.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/17","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/577"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1255.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1401","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1401.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1212","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9121,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10806}}","description":"SunOS 4.0.3 和 4.0.3c 版本中的 in.rlogind 服务存在本地提权漏洞，本地攻击者可利用 .rlogind 服务中的缓冲区溢出或权限校验缺陷，通过构造恶意参数或环境变量获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响运行受影响 SunOS 版本的 Sun 工作站和服务器，攻击者需具备本地账户访问权限，通过本地登录或远程 rlogin 连接触发漏洞，成功利用可完全控制目标系统获取 root 权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。Sun 公司已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1212"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1991-03-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:57.500","remediation":"建议升级至 SunOS 4.1.3 及以上版本并安装 Sun 官方安全补丁包（如 Patch 101945-02 for 4.1.3）。若无法升级，建议在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 rlogin/rsh 服务并重启 inetd 禁用 rlogind 服务，或在 /etc/hosts.deny 中添加 \"in.rlogind: ALL\" 限制访问，并配置防火墙阻断 513/514 端口作为临时缓解措施。建议尽快迁移至受支持的 Solaris 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1991-02.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/574","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1212.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/457d74301bd08d78bede177295a6ca646467d2a7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1212.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1212","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1212.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1212.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p8x2-4f73-49hw/GHSA-p8x2-4f73-49hw.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88643/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1212.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/joscanoga/Reto-python-CRM/blob/28c389209e3a121195f01b18344dd568da0600c5/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1401.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1399","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1399.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1211","title":"Sun SunOS in.telnetd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.1 及更早版本中的 in.telnetd 服务存在本地权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可利用 telnet 守护进程中的缓冲区溢出或权限校验缺陷，通过特制输入获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SunOS 4.1.1 及更早版本，要求攻击者具备本地账户访问权限，通过向 in.telnetd 发送特制数据触发缓冲区溢出或绕过权限检查，最终实现本地提权至 root 权限，CVSS 评分 7.2（高危）。Sun Microsystems 已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议升级至修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1211"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1991-03-27T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:57.387","remediation":"建议升级至 SunOS 4.1.2 或更高版本（已修复该漏洞），或迁移至 Oracle Solaris 现代版本。若无法升级，请立即禁用 in.telnetd 服务（注释 /etc/inetd.conf 中 telnet 行并重启 inetd），改用 SSH 进行远程管理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1991-02.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/574","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1211.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/067b58f5ad5d89a104fab4ddd25fa3685c59a18e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1211.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1211","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1211.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1211.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8cw7-xrv8-6v9v/GHSA-8cw7-xrv8-6v9v.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88649/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1211.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/joscanoga/Reto-python-CRM/blob/28c389209e3a121195f01b18344dd568da0600c5/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1399.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1430","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1430.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1258","title":"Sun SunOS RPC pwdauthd 远程信息泄露漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.1 及更早版本中的 rpc.pwdauthd 守护进程未正确限制远程访问权限，导致未经认证的远程攻击者可直接连接该服务并获取系统敏感信息（如用户账户信息等）。该漏洞利用门槛低，无需任何认证即可远程触发，影响所有运行受影响版本 SunOS 的系统。由于 rpc.pwdauthd 默认监听网络端口，攻击者可通过发送特制 RPC 请求实现信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1258"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1991-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.313","remediation":"升级到 Solaris 2.0 (SunOS 5.x) 或更高版本，该问题已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，应立即在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释或移除 rpc.pwdauthd 条目并重启 inetd 进程以禁用该服务，同时通过防火墙限制对 RPC 端口 111/tcp 和 111/udp 的访问，仅允许可信主机连接。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/102","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1782","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1258.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1258.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1258","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/248c2167e720df96125f6ac9925793063a207510/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1258.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1258.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qcjm-8xhv-v66h/GHSA-qcjm-8xhv-v66h.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87830/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1258.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000011.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1430.toml"}]